\begin_inset Formula $2D$
\end_inset

-dimensional real unit vector in 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathReal^{2D}$
\end_inset

, which is by definition 
\begin_inset Formula $\Sphere{2D-1}$
\end_inset

, the 
\begin_inset Formula $(2D-1)$
\end_inset

-sphere.
\end_layout

