\begin_inset Formula $\expval{\mathbf{O}}_{\mu_{1,2}}$
\end_inset

, are 
\begin_inset Formula $1.5$
\end_inset

 in the first case and 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

 in the second.
